Assemble the RPi5, flash OS, and plug in the camera

Install ffmpeg and mediamtx
sudo apt update && sudo apt install ffmpeg mediamtx -y

Copy the mediamtx.yml file from this repository to your Pi in the proper path

Replace the username and password

Install and enable Tailscale on the Pi and your viewing device
For the Pi: 
curl -fsSL https://tailscale.com/install.sh | sh
sudo tailscale up

Initialize mediamtx service
./mediamtx

Open VLC media player on the viewing device and utilize URL in the mediamtx file

